'''天主教迈阿密总教区'''是[[罗马天主教|罗马天主教]]在美国设立的一个[[总教区|总教区]]。其辖境包括[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]的[[布劳沃德县|布劳沃德县]]、[[迈阿密-戴德县|迈阿密-戴德县]]和[[门罗县_(佛罗里达州)|门罗县]]。总主教也担任该总教区的母堂——无玷圣母主教座堂的本堂神父。總教区拥有428位[[神父|神父]]、160位助祭、50位修士和300位修女，他们是各种天主教[[修会|修会]]的成员<ref name="paper">{{cite news| title=2007 Archdiocese of Miami Official Catholic Directory| pages=A4| publisher=The Florida Catholic Newspaper| date=2008-04-10}}</ref>。这些神父、助祭和男女修士服务于佛罗里达州南部118个[[堂区|堂区]]的130万天主教徒<ref name="anniversary"/>。現任總主教為{{link-en|多默·文斯基|Thomas Wenski}}<ref name="Wenski">{{cite web |title=Archbishop Thomas Wenski |url=https://www.miamiarch.org/CatholicDiocese.php?op=ArchbishopThomasWenski |publisher=Archdiocese of Miami |accessdate=2020-02-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200204201441/https://www.miamiarch.org/CatholicDiocese.php?op=ArchbishopThomasWenski |archivedate=2020-02-04 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>，輔理主教為{{link-en|亨利·德範·德爾加多|Enrique Esteban Delgado|亨利·德爾加多}}<ref>{{cite web |title=The Most * Rev. Enrique Delgado |url=https://www.miamiarch.org/CatholicDiocese.php?op=English_EnriqueDelgado |publisher=Archdiocese of Miami |accessdate=2020-02-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200204210429/https://www.miamiarch.org/CatholicDiocese.php?op=English_EnriqueDelgado |archivedate=2020-02-04 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休總主教為{{link-en|若望·法瓦羅拉|John Favalora|若望·克勉·法瓦羅拉}}<ref name="Favarola">{{cite web |title=Archbishop Emeritus of Miami |url=https://www.miamiarch.org/CatholicDiocese.php?op=ArchbishopJohnFavalora |publisher=Archdiocese of Miami |accessdate=2020-02-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200204202100/https://www.miamiarch.org/CatholicDiocese.php?op=ArchbishopJohnFavalora |archivedate=2020-02-04 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

由于存在大量移民，在该总教区的各个堂区，要提供至少一打语种的[[弥撒|弥撒]]<ref name="anniversary">{{cite web| publisher=South Florida Sun-Sentinel| title=Archdiocese is set for 50th anniversary| date=2007-10-06| url=http://www.sun-sentinel.com/features/columnists/sfl-liarchmiaminboct06,0,4168353.story| accessdate=2007-08-16}}{{dead link|date=2018年2月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。教育机构包括2所残疾儿童学校、60所小学、13所中学、2所大学<ref name="St Thomas University">{{cite web |last=Saint Thomas University |title=Saint Thomas University website |publisher=Saint Thomas University |url=http://www.stu.edu/ |accessdate=2007-08-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070814222008/http://www.stu.edu/ |archivedate=2007-08-14 }}</ref><ref name="Barry University">{{cite web |last=Barry University |title=Barry University website |publisher=Barry University |url=http://www.barry.edu/default.htm |accessdate=2007-08-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070813090440/http://barry.edu/default.htm |archivedate=2007-08-13 }}</ref>和2所修院<ref name="Vincent">{{cite web| last=St. Vincent De Paul Seminary| title=St Vincent De Paul Regional Seminary website| publisher=St. Vincent De Paul Seminary| url=http://www.universities.com/On-Campus/Saint_Vincent_De_Paul_Regional_Seminary.html| accessdate=2007-08-16| archive-date=2007-09-28| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070928020027/http://www.universities.com/On-Campus/Saint_Vincent_De_Paul_Regional_Seminary.html| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="JohnV">{{cite web| last=St. John Vianney Seminary| title=St John Vianney Seminary website| publisher=St. John Vianney Seminary| url=http://www.collegeview.com/school/school_hub.jsp?scid=5000209| accessdate=2007-08-16| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070929090256/http://www.collegeview.com/school/school_hub.jsp?scid=5000209| archivedate=2007-09-29}}</ref><ref name="recruits">{{cite web |last=Arbiteronline.com |title=Catholic Leaders Seek Young Religious Recruits On The Web |url=http://media.www.arbiteronline.com/media/storage/paper890/news/2007/08/30/Biztech/Catholic.Leaders.Seek.Young.Religious.Recruits.On.The.Web-2942827.shtml |accessdate=2007-09-25 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090720030746/http://media.www.arbiteronline.com/media/storage/paper890/news/2007/08/30/Biztech/Catholic.Leaders.Seek.Young.Religious.Recruits.On.The.Web-2942827.shtml |archivedate=2009-07-20 }}</ref>。该总教区还拥有和运营广播、印刷和电视媒体，进行补充教导、交流和尽职<ref name="crossroads">{{cite news| publisher=Miami Herald| title=Miami Archdiocese at a Crossroads in 50th year| date=2007-10-07| url=http://www.miamiherald.com/457/story/263201.html#recent_comm| accessdate=2007-10-07}}</ref>。 

该总教区开办的社会服务机构包括2所医院、9个保健中心、3个安老院和2个公墓<ref name="paper"/>。慈善机构包括流浪者收容所、贫困者法律服务、生命权利中心（艾滋病服务）、仁爱修会（Missionaries of Charity）和圣文生德保修会（Society of Saint Vincent de Paul）援助穷人的工作<ref name="Camillus"/><ref name="legal"/><ref name="hiv"/><ref name="mcharity"/><ref name="society"/>。迈阿密总教区的天主教慈善会（Catholic Charities），是总教区开办的一个单独的非盈利机构。它自称为佛罗里达州南部最大的服务于贫困者的非政府组织<ref name="paper" /><ref name="whoweare">{{Cite web|url=http://www.catholiccharitiesadm.org/who_we_are.htm|title=Catholic Charities Who We Are|accessdate=2007-10-08|publisher=Archdiocese of Miami Catholic Charities|year=2007|author=Archdiocese of Miami|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070731135652/http://www.catholiccharitiesadm.org/who_we_are.htm|archive-date=2007-07-31|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

==历史==
1958年以前，整个佛罗里达州都属于天主教圣奥古斯丁教区。在1950年代和1960年代初，圣奥古斯丁总主教{{link-en|若瑟·巴特利爵·赫尔利|Joseph Patrick Hurley}}预料人口將會大幅增加，便在佛罗里达州南部各处购买土地<ref>{{cite web |last=Gannon |first=Michael |title=The Builder Bishop |publisher=Saint Augustine Catholic |date=2007-10-30 |url=http://www.staugcatholic.org/feature2.shtml |accessdate=2007-10-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070715202643/http://www.staugcatholic.org/feature2.shtml |archivedate=2007-07-15 }}</ref>今天，这些曾经偏僻的地区已经成为繁荣的城市。在赫尔利主教购买的土地上建起了许多天主教教堂、学校和公墓。<ref name="anniversary" />

迈阿密教区成立于1958年10月7日，{{link-en|高尔孟·卡罗尔|Coleman Carroll}}就任[[主教|主教]]。该教区包括佛罗里达州南部的16个县，有天主教徒20万人，占全州天主教徒的一半。教区成立不到一年以后，[[菲德尔·卡斯特罗|菲德尔·卡斯特罗]]在[[古巴|古巴]]掌权。这引发了大批古巴人逃往佛罗里达州南部。卡罗尔主教成立了天主教福利局，在帮助古巴移民的浪潮中扮演了重要角色。从1960年到1962年，14,000名古巴儿童被送往美国。Bryan O. Walsh蒙席策划了彼得潘行动（Operation Pedro Pan），将他们安置在朋友、亲戚或者天主教福利局。1996年，天主教福利局更名为天主教慈善会。今天自称是佛罗里达州南部最大的提供社会服务的非政府机构。到2006年，它服务于[[布劳沃德县|布劳沃德县]]、[[戴德县|戴德县]]和[[门罗县_(佛罗里达州)|门罗县]]3县区域的17,000户家庭<ref>{{cite web| last=Catholic Charities| title=Catholic Charities History| publisher=Catholic Charities| url=http://www.catholiccharitiesadm.org/who_we_are.htm| accessdate=2007-08-16| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070731135652/http://www.catholiccharitiesadm.org/who_we_are.htm| archive-date=2007-07-31| dead-url=yes}}</ref>。
[[File:Mariel_Refugees.jpg|thumb]]期间搭乘拥挤的小船抵达的古巴难民]]

由于人口的增长，该教区在1968年分设教区。有8个县成为天主教圣彼得斯堡教区和新成立的天主教奥兰多教区的一部分。迈阿密教区被[[教宗保禄六世|教宗保禄六世]]升为总教区。1968年3月2日，卡罗尔升任总主教<ref name="history">{{cite web|url=http://www.miamiarchdiocese.org/ip.asp?op=A152500&lg=E|title=Archdiocese of Miami: History - Made an Archdiocese|author=Miami Archdiocese|publisher=Miami Archdiocese|accessdate=2007-04-20|archive-date=2012-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120217102317/http://www.miamiarchdiocese.org/ip.asp?op=A152500&lg=E|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1963年，卡罗尔主教在天主教学校中废除了[[种族隔离|种族隔离]]，而佛罗里达州的公立学校直到1970年代初才实现废止种族歧视<ref>{{cite web |last=The Florida Memory Project |title=Florida Timeline |publisher=The Florida Memory Project |url=http://www.floridamemory.com/Timeline/ |accessdate=2007-11-10 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070404222720/http://www.floridamemory.com/Timeline/ |archivedate=2007-04-04 }}</ref>。他参加了[[梵蒂冈第二屆大公会议|梵蒂冈第二屆大公会议]]的教会改革<ref name="anniversary" />。

1977年7月26日卡罗尔主教去世，{{link-en|愛德華·A·麥卡錫|Edward A. McCarthy|爱德华·安多尼·麦卡锡}}被任命为迈阿密教区总主教。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.miamiarchdiocese.org/ip.asp?op=A153000&lg=El|title=Archdiocese of Miami: History - First Successor|author=Miami Archdiocese|publisher=Miami Archdiocese|accessdate=2007-05-26|archive-date=2012-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120206144115/http://www.miamiarchdiocese.org/ip.asp?op=A153000&lg=El|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="McCarthy">{{cite web |url=http://www.mccarthyhigh.org/about.html |title=Archbishop McCarthy High School - About Us |author=McCarthy High School |publisher=McCarthy High School |accessdate=2007-05-26 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070428015121/http://www.mccarthyhigh.org/about.html |archivedate=2007-04-28 }}</ref>麦卡锡监督总教区Pastoral中心的建造<!-- 重建 most senior operational divisions. 他建立了Office of [[Lay_Ecclesial_Ministry|Lay Ecclesial Ministry]], the Office of [[Evangelization|Evangelization]]和助祭 program.1980年，他提议支持和援助 during [[Mariel_Boat_Lift|Mariel Boat Lift]]. -->。次年，他支持因「湿脚、乾脚政策」被拘留的[[海地|海地]]移民的权利。应对这些新移民的需要，他开放了Pierre Toussaint海地人天主教中心。<ref name="McCarthy" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.miamiarchdiocese.org/ip.asp?op=A154500&lg=E|title=Archdiocese of Miami: History - More Exiles|author=Miami Archdiocese|publisher=Miami Archdiocese|accessdate=2007-04-19|archive-date=2012-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120206144012/http://www.miamiarchdiocese.org/ip.asp?op=A154500&lg=E|dead-url=no}}</ref>1994年，年已75岁的麦卡锡主教退休<ref name="anniversary" />。

1994年11月3日，[[教宗若望·保禄二世|教宗若望·保禄二世]]任命{{link-en|若望·法瓦罗拉|John Favalora|若望·克勉·法瓦羅拉}}為迈阿密总教区总主教。在其任职期间，创建了2所中学和9所小学。法瓦罗拉还发起5年筹款活动，来支持总教区的天主教教育机构。这次捐款筹集到9000万美元。<ref name="anniversary" />2003年7月11日，若望·保禄二世任命迈阿密教区助理主教{{link-en|多默·文斯基|Thomas Wenski|多默·吉拉·文斯基}}领导[[天主教奥兰多教区|天主教奥兰多教区]]<ref name="usatoday">{{cite web| last=Grossman| first=Cathy Lynn| title=Vacancies Occupy Catholic Church| publisher=USA Today| date=2003-07-23| url=http://www.snapnetwork.org/news/vatican/vacancies_occupy.htm| accessdate=2007-08-16| archive-date=2020-09-26| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926125151/https://www.snapnetwork.org/news/vatican/vacancies_occupy.htm| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="usatoday2">{{cite web| last=Grossman| first=Cathy Lynn| title=Church vacancies will leave room at the top of dioceses| publisher=USA Today| date=2003-07-23| url=http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/USAToday/access/354000471.html?dids=354000471:354000471&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&date=Jul+2%2C+2003&author=Cathy+Lynn+Grossman&pub=USA+TODAY&edition=&startpage=D.08&desc=Church+vacancies+will+leave+room+at+the+top+of+dioceses| accessdate=2007-08-16| archive-date=2012-10-18| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121018071841/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/USAToday/access/354000471.html?dids=354000471:354000471&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&date=Jul+2,+2003&author=Cathy+Lynn+Grossman&pub=USA+TODAY&edition=&startpage=D.08&desc=Church+vacancies+will+leave+room+at+the+top+of+dioceses| dead-url=no}}</ref>。佛罗里达南部地区接纳的大批移民来自天主教占绝对优势的中南美洲，因此天主教徒占总人口的25%。来自世界其他地区，包括亚洲和非洲国家的移民潮，则使得整个总教区各个堂区的弥撒需要以超过一打不同的语言来进行<ref name="anniversary" /><ref>{{cite web| last=Florida Trend| title=Population Still Growing| publisher=Trend Magazines Inc.| url=http://www.floridatrend.com/data_article.asp?cName=Florida%20Data&rName=Demographics&whatID=1&aID=452637502.3046781.607204.5270478.2256005.470&aID2=46699| accessdate=2007-09-25| archive-date=2012-02-18| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120218110746/http://www.floridatrend.com/data_article.asp?cName=Florida%20Data&rName=Demographics&whatID=1&aID=452637502.3046781.607204.5270478.2256005.470&aID2=46699| dead-url=no}}</ref>。

